               # Startup Idea Generator
Transform your ideas into potential million-dollar startup concepts using AI 

                 # Overview
Startup Idea Generator ek web-based application hai jo user ke input problem ko analyze karke uske liye unique startup ideas generate karta hai.
Ye project hackathon ke liye design kiya gaya hai jisme AI ka use karke innovation ko boost kiya gaya hai.

                
                 # Features
* Problem-based idea generation
* Fast AI-powered responses
* Interactive dashboard
* Clean and modern UI
* Dynamic content loading
* Project Structure
startup_generating_idea/
│
├── templates/
│   ├── index.html        # Landing page
│   └── dashboard.html    # Main dashboard
│
├── static/
│   ├── style.css         # Styling
│   └── script.js         # Frontend logic
│
└── app.py ( backend)

   # Tech Stack
* HTML5
* CSS3
* JavaScript
* Flask (Python backend)
* AI API (Groq / OpenAI)

  # How It Works
1). User apni problem input karta hai
2). Frontend se request backend ko jati hai
3). Backend AI API ko call karta hai
4). AI ek startup idea generate karta hai
5). Result dashboard par display hota hai
